<div>
<h2>Scope and Usage</h2>
<p>
The Remittance resource provides application level error or application level adjudication results which are the result of processing a submitted 
disciplineClaim which is the functional corollary of a Claim, Pre-Determination or a Pre-Authorization.

The Remittance resource is the response for the submission of: OralHealthClaim, VisionClaim ... as well as ReversalRequests.

